Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了 說笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是與我緊緊地纏繞的話不行喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.59,0:22:38.57,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.27,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.52,0:22:49.69,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.82,0:22:55.57,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇蹟也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.16,0:23:08.48,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.00,0:23:19.51,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.76,0:23:27.77,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能   太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.15,0:23:33.07,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.51,0:23:44.18,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.94,0:00:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是深山的五重塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.66,0:00:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說的力量 不可能的犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.21,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的五重塔傳說(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.12,0:01:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候也該出來到郊外走一走才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.71,0:02:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧小蘭姐姐參加雜誌猜謎得了獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.29,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過解開謎底的人不是柯南你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是簡單的要死的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.99,0:02:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 這種沉悶的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.42,0:02:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道這種觀光旅行一定沒什麼好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始聽到可以去旅行自己還高興的不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回飯店去泡個澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 這裏是禁煙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.71,0:02:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對旅行的人來講這種地方的確很無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.13,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種地方 我們在都市生活根本不能常常來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.06,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種可以清淨心靈的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是難得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼年輕竟然能講出這麼棒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.83,0:03:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我帶你們到寺裏面參觀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.05,0:03:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用把我算上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣太沒禮貌了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座寺廟在四百年前修建完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經四百年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.58,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是古老啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是古老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.31,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它還見證著歷史的轉變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如五重塔的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.85,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個從江戶時代開始就一直使用的舊井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在不用了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它突然乾枯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是一個失戀的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在井前哭了三天三夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.09,0:03:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些眼淚就和井水一起全部消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒謬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個五重塔有一個可怕的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼傳說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在江戶時代初期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持看中了一個年輕有為的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.84,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為他可以繼承下一任的住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.58,0:04:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他愛上村長的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來他就觸犯寺規和村長的女兒私奔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖物的老鷹將年輕人給帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.24,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他給吊在五重塔的塔上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在江戶時代中期的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個心術不正的住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將寺廟的貴重物品給偷偷賣掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都沉溺於酒樂之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某一天他突然失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.64,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了幾天之後被發現吊死在五重塔的前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後大家就開始傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人觸犯寺規就會受到五重塔的詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.48,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要露出這麼可怕的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡…淡海大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這個寺廟的住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.13,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次派大人帶著小孩到底來這裏做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.61,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是純粹來觀光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是可疑人物 不可以相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓外面的人擅自進來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是觀光是本寺的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這事情整個寺廟被搶走了 難道你忘記了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.42,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那些人到最後一定會遭天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報應降臨的天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.75,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是這座寺廟變成觀光公司的物產了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.89,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近準備要建造一個主題公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼附近就要改變了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持說是被他們給騙了 一直在反對著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.67,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他對觀光客都是那種態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然胡亂嚇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我爸爸很喜歡生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.91,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是這邊不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父親該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那個有名的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我可以跟我的孫子誇耀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們太榮幸了 竟然還招待我們吃晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.61,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮幸的應該是我們才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個酒店剛開業不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.46,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果毛利先生這種名人出現會是個很好的宣傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.44,0:07:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我可以派上用場的話我很樂意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.06,0:07:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個酒店真是又豪華又漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年這個時候我所推薦的主題公園就會完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就會更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這次工程花費不少吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多八十億元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.06,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成之後 一年要賺數百億是不成問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記自我介紹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這間酒店的經理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在這裏丟人現眼了 尾村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且名偵探毛利先生來住宿的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要岡部講才會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.45,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太差勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給我反省一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你今天不是要去東京嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有時間在這裏講話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了 我太激動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚴格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.74,0:08:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是在工作方面就會毫不留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你領帶夾上的是鑽石嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒有什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是小小五克拉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有五克拉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不要這樣 很丟臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人類最真實的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫做真實嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 這是你要的雪茄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收據呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這樣我怎麼能報帳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.92,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你一直都拿著這麼多錢到處走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 這只是一部分而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我討厭用信用卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這裏悠閒地用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是幻塊寺的和尚嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的修煉已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用政治手段欺騙我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為這樣我就會甘休的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為了這個回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要亂講…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我和你爸爸仔細商量過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.60,0:10:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓寺廟能繼續經營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說"暫時把寺廟的所有權交出來這樣比較好辦事"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我爸爸就這樣相信了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.58,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我會遵循法律的方法和你打官司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說的只有這些嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.88,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正在會客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天到我的辦公室再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別以為我會就這樣罷手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜事一直來煩心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生和寺廟的人之間有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些無聊的小問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們把這偉大的觀光開發計畫給想歪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我要把神聖的寺廟給毀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些無聊的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於觀光的收入 那個寺廟也會因此得益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群無知的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打那個寺廟歪主意的話會招來報應吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能說這個啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那個寺廟的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.31,0:11:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣也有不少人跑來勸過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過正因如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.72,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻覺得可以利用做招引客人的免費廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是毛利偵探事務所…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.32,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是岡部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天寺院的嚮導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.96,0:11:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報應真的發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你說報應發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請馬上到寺廟這邊來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 快點 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微說明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個很可怕的報應發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(誦經)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼報應嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是晨課而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.54,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑑定方面的工作完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.95,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在準備要把屍體給拿下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體是在五重塔的五樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在欄杆綁上繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.13,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一邊繞過屋頂的前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後吊下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.16,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份應該是經營觀光公司的小田英明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.68,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有個不認識的偵探正在上面做確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探 是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 橫溝刑事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是毛利先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼會來這裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為某些緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言歸正傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個案件你有什麼意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照情況來說應該是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自殺方式很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻沒有被殺的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼講的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 小田先生擁有大約一百公斤的巨型體積
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把他帶到五樓上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人是做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算可以把他給搬上去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓梯通道非常的狹窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人要進出已經很不容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然拉上去是有可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過衣服就會被弄髒 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體也會有擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.73,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛去看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有這些痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你已經調查這麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼會吊在那裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欄杆上有新的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條繩子是新的卻到處都有燒焦的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.24,0:14:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼讓他下來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳根本墊不到地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果腳踩不到欄杆的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你怎麼可以到這種地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找廁所結果迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來廁所並不在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.91,0:15:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 到底在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小孩是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據鑑定人員的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五重塔裏面沒有什麼灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無法確認有沒有小田的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有請這鎮上的醫生檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生並沒有外傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為頸部受到壓迫而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.08,0:15:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說頸部被勒是直接致死的原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.52,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推定死亡的時間是凌晨三點到四點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.63,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田將酒店的總統套房當作自己的家在使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌晨兩點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫃檯的人看見他走了出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照時間來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.83,0:15:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是直接到這裏來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺書呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 你為什麼這麼傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.79,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你可以…可以再等一下的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了 請問你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.34,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是0DA酒店的經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫尾村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你好像不在這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 突然被派去出差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有什麼頭緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他自殺的動機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去出差是為了籌募資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這次失敗的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.07,0:16:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本公司在這個月底就必須結業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過社長他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我還更加難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他昨天還帶了一大筆錢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長很重視自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓別人看到他的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有時候還會死撐場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺廟方面講要尋求法律方面來對付他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以社長非常的在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大叔的錢包不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.94,0:17:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者身上的物件並沒有錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生也沒有換過衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天帶的錢包竟然不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  既然要自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶那麼多錢出來幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.99,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是常常叫你別在現場亂晃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個領帶夾也不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.16,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以妨礙大人他們進行調查啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.24,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 柯南講的領帶夾是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生昨晚夾在領帶上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個華麗的鑲著五克拉鑽石的領帶夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的確沒有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.33,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說被搶劫的可能性也很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是遇到強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自己已經想自我了斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就這樣乖乖的把錢財拿出來給強盜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.64,0:18:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這件事根本不是自殺的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是被別人勒死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被勒的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會因為很痛苦而用手去做拉扯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 手上並沒有痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這真的是被殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.23,0:18:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼將被害者吊到那麼高的五重塔的前端呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了自殺之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能是人為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.23,0:18:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的是有犯人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是神的報應了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.64,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神對不尊敬的人做的懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是靜岡警局的橫溝刑事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你們是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿這個樣子也看不出來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這個寺廟的住持 淡海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的兒子 春海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這裏的工人 岡部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位在凌晨三點到四點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.41,0:19:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了些什麼事情 可以告訴我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是自殺的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.24,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 現在還不能確定 而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.48,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生身上的財物可能被人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道吃齋唸佛的我們會去偷東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.56,0:19:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 為了參考我必須知道你們當時在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.28,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那件事情讓我實在是很生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以當時我在大堂裏面讀經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀經…你正在念經嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那麼晚的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個預感會有聖物的報應出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報應嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 春海先生昵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在睡覺 五點鐘起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後岡部就跑來通知我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說小田出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我非常驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我也馬上打電話給毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.78,0:20:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不先打電話報警而是先打電話給毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這傢伙是小田的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.21,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他把小田介紹給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡…淡海大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽信了小田社長的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.64,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果增加觀光客 這裏的香油錢也會增加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.16,0:20:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被他給騙了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個住持好像被小田先生騙了這裏的所有權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.18,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你們三人都很恨小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算恨他又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那位名偵探講過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田除了自殺之外不可能是他殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺的話根本就沒有犯人不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.86,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…還沒有斷定就是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.39,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就快點做出決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.58,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想因為那骯髒的傢伙把這個神聖之地給玷汙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.61,0:21:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的錢包和領帶夾都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在這種狀況來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了自殺之外別無它想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.98,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手肘的部位髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是草的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是倒下去的時候手肘擦到了草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙腳的後腳跟都有泥土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這裏會有泥土的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.19,0:21:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看上面有燒焦的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.27,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.82,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.69,0:21:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是領帶夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.77,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.09,0:22:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的第一現場就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的假設是正確的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生並不是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.10,0:22:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.37,0:22:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人大概就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.42,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候講了那句話的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.38,0:22:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.62,0:23:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能站在欄杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣要怎麼自殺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.56,0:23:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我把他當作是被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.76,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過距離五十公分那麼遠的繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.93,0:24:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是怎麼把它吊上去的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.93,0:24:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.59,0:24:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是綁在欄杆上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.38,0:24:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會打個活結呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.97,0:24:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.44,0:24:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的五重塔傳說(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.03,0:24:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.63,0:24:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.28,0:24:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次是後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.50,0:24:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說的真相可能更加恐怖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.25,0:24:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
